{"tid":223331,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"1985-1995出世既香港男性算唔算最悲慘既一代","createTime":"2017-04-30T09:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T10:22:24.000Z","uid":57205,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aab259817320d47e50e2f17c912587e2f2c83c71","tid":223331,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"而家出街見D後生女，心口就算唔係導彈咁大<br />\n起馬對波都會有肉，你會知道係一個女性<br />\n<br />\n1985-1995呢十年出世既男性，中學時期既女同學全部係平到成塊版<br />\n多得鄭秀文同阿SA呢兩條臭西宣揚平胸主義<br />\n果個時期有波會俾人笑<br />\n<br />\n新一代就知道身材既重要性，所以出街見到真係好感慨<br />\n點解我要咁慘係呢十年出世<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a15421f1201fb9f19b9d006bec6f4b97c85485","tid":223331,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"關撚事咩 你係勁既 而家都食緊18歲妹妹仔啦"},{"pid":"c082786fc84da311c89b81d046ff5e2949070c75","tid":223331,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"識親啲女都超大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e683e5fd004ce205e57837d6a32669e5d3a5cee7","tid":223331,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關撚事咩 你係勁既 而家都食緊18歲妹妹仔啦</blockquote><br />\n出黎做野識女仔都搵返咁上下年紀架啦<br />\n結婚唔通搵個18歲妹妹咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/face